"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The reports of attacks on commercial ships came after the US said it destroyed 16 Iranian mine-layers in the area. This has increased tensions in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ship Attacks Increase Tensions\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los reportes de ataques a barcos comerciales llegaron despu\u00e9s de que Estados Unidos dijo que destruy\u00f3 16 barcos iran\u00edes en el \u00e1rea. Esto ha aumentado las tensiones en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques a Barcos Aumentan Tensi\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Two drones were shot down near Dubai airport. This incident raises concerns about security and safety in the area.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drones Shot Down Near Dubai\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dos drones fueron derribados cerca del aeropuerto de Dub\u00e1i. Este incidente causa preocupaci\u00f3n sobre la seguridad en el \u00e1rea.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Derriban Drones en Dub\u00e1i\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"President Putin is trying to act as a mediator in international conflicts, but it is a difficult task.\",            \"english_title\": \"Putin as Mediator\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente Putin est\u00e1 tratando de ser mediador en conflictos internacionales, pero es una tarea dif\u00edcil.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Putin como Mediador\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The biggest evacuation in the city's history happened after a British flying bomb was found near a collapsed bridge.\",            \"english_title\": \"City's Biggest Evacuation\",            \"translated_version\": \"La evacuaci\u00f3n m\u00e1s grande en la historia de la ciudad ocurri\u00f3 despu\u00e9s de que se encontr\u00f3 una bomba voladora brit\u00e1nica cerca de un puente ca\u00eddo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Gran Evacuaci\u00f3n en la Ciudad\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Police are investigating the cause of a fire in the western Fribourg canton, which injured several people.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fire Investigation in Fribourg\",            \"translated_version\": \"La polic\u00eda est\u00e1 investigando la causa de un incendio en el cant\u00f3n occidental de Friburgo, que hiri\u00f3 a varias personas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Investigaci\u00f3n de Incendio en Friburgo\"        }    ]}"